---
// Importamos los estilos del Búnker
import '../styles/global.css';

// BlackHorse Landing - Sovereign Tech
const githubLink = "https://github.com/MartinCajiao/BlackHorse/releases/tag/v1.0.0";
const linkedinLink = "https://www.linkedin.com/in/martincajiao/";
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>BLACKHORSE | SOVEREIGN AI</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		
		<div class="fixed inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-zinc-900/20 via-[#050505] to-[#050505] -z-10"></div>

		<main class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 pt-24 pb-12 text-center">
			
			<div class="mb-10 group cursor-default">
				<h1 class="text-7xl md:text-[9rem] font-black tracking-tighter italic leading-none">
					<span class="text-metallic">BLACK</span><span class="text-glow">HORSE</span>
				</h1>
				<div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mt-8 opacity-80">
					<div class="h-[1px] w-8 md:w-16 bg-zinc-800"></div>
					<p class="text-zinc-400 font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[10px] md:text-xs">
						Offline Core // No Cloud // No Spyware
					</p>
					<div class="h-[1px] w-8 md:w-16 bg-zinc-800"></div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="max-w-2xl relative z-10">
				<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-zinc-400 font-light leading-relaxed mb-12">
					Intelligence shouldn't ask for permission. 
					<span class="text-white font-medium">100% Local.</span> No tracking. No subscriptions. 
					Built for raw efficiency in private environments.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 w-full max-w-md relative z-10">
				<a href={githubLink} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary">Download .EXE</a>
				<a href={linkedinLink} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-secondary">Creator</a>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-24 w-full max-w-4xl text-left relative z-10 group">
				<div class="absolute -inset-[1px] bg-gradient-to-r from-zinc-800 via-zinc-600 to-zinc-800 opacity-20 group-hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
				<div class="relative bg-[#080808] border border-zinc-800 p-6 font-mono text-xs sm:text-sm shadow-2xl">
					<div class="flex gap-2 mb-4">
						<div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-zinc-700"></div>
						<div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-zinc-700"></div>
						<div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-zinc-700"></div>
					</div>
					<p class="text-zinc-500 mb-2">> root@blackhorse-ltsc:~# ./engine --init-core</p>
					<p class="text-zinc-400">[OK] Native <span class="text-white font-bold">Rust</span> processing engine detected.</p>
					<p class="text-zinc-400">[OK] Local memory management secured.</p>
					<p class="text-zinc-600">...</p>
					<p class="text-red-900/80 uppercase tracking-widest">[!] Warning: External connection blocked for security.</p>
					<p class="text-zinc-400">[OK] Initiating Sovereignty Mode (Air-Gapped).</p>
					<p class="text-white mt-4 font-bold">> Engine: Ready. Awaiting brain_ <span class="animate-pulse">█</span></p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-16 w-full max-w-4xl border border-zinc-900 bg-zinc-950/50 p-8 md:p-12 text-left relative z-10">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-black italic tracking-tighter text-white mb-6 uppercase flex items-center gap-3 text-glow">
					🧠 Neural Core Setup <span class="text-zinc-600 font-light font-sans tracking-normal text-sm normal-case ml-2">(Critical Steps)</span>
				</h2>
				<p class="text-zinc-400 mb-8 font-light text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
					BlackHorse is a universal reader. To activate it, you must drop the models into the system's internal folder:
				</p>

				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
					<div class="border-l border-zinc-800 pl-6">
						<h3 class="text-white font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-[0.1em] mb-3">01. Document Analysis (RAG)</h3>
						<p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">Required to index your local knowledge base.</p>
						<ul class="text-zinc-400 space-y-3 font-mono text-xs">
							<li class="flex gap-2">
								<span class="text-zinc-600">></span> 
								<span>Download the <span class="text-white">all-MiniLM-L6-v2</span> folder from the repo.</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex gap-2">
								<span class="text-zinc-600">></span> 
								<span>Inside BlackHorse, click the <strong class="text-white">Folder Icon</strong> in Settings.</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex gap-2">
								<span class="text-zinc-600">></span> 
								<span>This will open <span class="text-zinc-300 italic">AppData/models</span>. Paste the folder there.</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div class="border-l border-zinc-800 pl-6">
						<h3 class="text-white font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-[0.1em] mb-3">02. Neural Chat (LLM)</h3>
						<p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">The fallback model ensures stability during complex tasks.</p>
						
						<div class="bg-[#050505] p-4 border border-zinc-800 relative group">
							<p class="text-zinc-500 text-[10px] font-bold mb-2 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Recommended Fallback</p>
							<a href="https://huggingface.co/models" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-white hover:text-zinc-300 transition-colors text-xs font-mono break-all inline-block mb-3 border-b border-zinc-700 pb-1">
								Meta-Llama-3-8B-Instruct.Q2_K.gguf
							</a>
							<p class="text-zinc-400 text-xs font-light leading-relaxed">
								Download it and paste it directly into the same <span class="italic text-white">AppData/models</span> folder you opened in the previous step.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-20 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-left max-w-5xl relative z-10">
				<article class="p-8 border border-zinc-900 bg-zinc-950/40 hover:border-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-900/60 transition-all duration-500 group">
					<h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-4 uppercase text-xs tracking-[0.2em] flex items-center gap-3">
						<span class="text-zinc-700 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-500">01.</span> Sovereignty
					</h3>
					<p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">Your data never leaves your RAM. Bunker-level privacy by design. You are the sole owner of your intelligence.</p>
				</article>

				<article class="p-8 border border-zinc-900 bg-zinc-950/40 hover:border-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-900/60 transition-all duration-500 group">
					<h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-4 uppercase text-xs tracking-[0.2em] flex items-center gap-3">
						<span class="text-zinc-700 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-500">02.</span> Performance
					</h3>
					<p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">Rust core engineered for maximum speed. No network latency, no waiting on third-party servers.</p>
				</article>

				<article class="p-8 border border-zinc-900 bg-zinc-950/40 hover:border-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-900/60 transition-all duration-500 group">
					<h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-4 uppercase text-xs tracking-[0.2em] flex items-center gap-3">
						<span class="text-zinc-700 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-500">03.</span> Ownership
					</h3>
					<p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm leading-relaxed font-light">Zero external dependencies. The executable belongs to you. Technology designed for free men.</p>
				</article>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-12 w-full max-w-5xl border-y border-zinc-900 py-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8 md:gap-16 opacity-60">
				<div class="text-center">
					<p class="text-white font-bold text-lg">Zero</p>
					<p class="text-zinc-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Telemetry</p>
				</div>
				<div class="text-center">
					<p class="text-white font-bold text-lg">Rust</p>
					<p class="text-zinc-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Powered</p>
				</div>
				<div class="text-center">
					<p class="text-white font-bold text-lg">LTSC</p>
					<p class="text-zinc-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Native</p>
				</div>
				<div class="text-center">
					<p class="text-white font-bold text-lg">GGUF</p>
					<p class="text-zinc-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Universal</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-12 w-full max-w-3xl border border-zinc-800/50 bg-[#080808]/50 p-4 rounded-sm text-left relative z-10">
				<p class="text-zinc-500 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">> SYSTEM LOG // BETA_NOTICE 🇪🇨</p>
				<p class="text-zinc-400 text-xs font-light leading-relaxed">
					BlackHorse is proudly engineered by an Ecuadorian DEV. Because of this, you might spot some UI elements or logs still speaking Spanish. I will patch it in the next build—forgive the dust while we ride through this Beta!
				</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="mt-16 w-full max-w-5xl opacity-40">
				<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
					<p class="text-[10px] text-zinc-500 font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.4em]">Engineered by Martin Cajiao // 2026</p>
					<p class="text-[10px] text-zinc-500 font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.4em]">Rust Core // Windows LTSC Ready</p>
				</div>
			</footer>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>